{"tid":1691623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[推到有人跟進]又一隻眼","createTime":"2019-11-03T17:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:27:22.000Z","uid":70124,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"243702117f42a9c1dcd2fd2e40286ab950c94092","tid":1691623,"uid":70124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:36:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">53歲男右眼受傷留院　疑被催淚彈擊中</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">【01:20】據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\">53歲男子在廣華醫院治理後轉送明愛醫院，男子右眼球破裂</span>。<br />\n<br />\n【00:05】10月31日晚上約8時30分，一名於太子站B1出口附近的中年男子爆眼受傷，急救員上前治理為其止血時，男子不斷稱他只是在附近與人聊天。有人替他召救護車。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，一名男子留院，情況嚴重。據了解，傷者為53歲右眼受傷的男子，疑被催淚彈擊中。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/paNrPsk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpaNrPsk.jpg&h=ee134e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191101/s00001/1572537781337/【831太子站兩個月-短片】53歲男右眼受傷留院-疑被催淚彈擊中\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191101%2Fs00001%2F1572537781337%2F%E3%80%90831%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%9153%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%B3%E7%9C%BC%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2-%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=6347c9b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191101%2Fs00001%2F1572537781337%2F%E3%80%90831%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%9153%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%B3%E7%9C%BC%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2-%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD&h=9c9ca3b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191101/s00001/1572537781337/【831太子站兩個月-短片】53歲男右眼受傷留院-疑被催淚彈擊中</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"